Show HN: Moongarlic – understand how much money you make
text:
Hi,

I'm hoping to get some feedback on a tool I'm working on that helps people understand compensation packages that include equity, which are often confusing. After you enter the details of your package, it will create a graph and table breaking down your annual compensation in $$$. You can also compare your existing compensation to a new job offer. The tool is free and your data isn't saved unless you sign in.

What do you think? Is something like this useful?
